1
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:28,000
=Ancient Love Poetry=

2
00:01:31,194 --> 00:01:33,083
=Episod 2=

3
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:35,160
Tak sangka saya masih perlu
buat kerja Pu Hua

4
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:36,950
biarpun dah masuk ke Istana Chang Yuan.

5
00:01:38,230 --> 00:01:39,230
Ini di luar jangkaan saya.

6
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:42,870
Beritahu saya,

7
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:45,760
mengapa kamu suka Ketulan Ais?

8
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,270
Apa kelebihan dia?

9
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,040
Saya tak faham.

10
00:01:58,270 --> 00:01:58,760
Sudahlah.

11
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,230
Memandangkan kamu begini ikhlas,

12
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,760
saya patut buat sesuatu
yang baik untuk kamu.

13
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,080
Terima kasih, Yang Amat Mulia.

14
00:02:22,390 --> 00:02:23,390
Dewa Agung, sila minum teh.

15
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,190
Hong Ri, ke tepi.

16
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,270
Tak nak.

17
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,190
Kalau begitu, jangan salahkan kami.

18
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:10,880
Dewa Agung, saya dah buat
tiga sekatan.

19
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,800
Tak tahulah bagaimana mereka masuk.

20
00:03:18,390 --> 00:03:20,470
Di mana Shang Gu? Belum balikkah?

21
00:03:21,270 --> 00:03:23,360
Sejak awak beri Yang Amat Mulia

22
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,880
soalan tentang Puak Syaitan,

23
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:26,800
dia pernah datang beberapa kali,

24
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:28,240
tapi tak pernah duduk lama.

25
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:31,440
Mungkin sedang cari jawapan
untuk soalan awak.

26
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,440
Kemaskan barang,
pergi ke Alam Bawah esok.

27
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:38,910
Awak tak mahu hadiri
jamuan hari jadi Yang Amat Mulia?

28
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:40,600
Saya tak suka suasana meriah.

29
00:03:41,270 --> 00:03:44,240
Namun, awak patut pergi menyapanya.

30
00:03:53,110 --> 00:03:53,800
Pagi tadi,

31
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,470
saya yang ambilkan Dewa Agung
air cuci muka.

32
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,360
Dewa Agung juga tengok saya
untuk beberapa kali.

33
00:03:57,670 --> 00:03:58,720
Jangan berlagak.

34
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,520
Saya pernah tengok
tulisan tangan Dewa Agung.

35
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:01,720
Pernahkah kamu tengok?

36
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:03,080
Semasa Dewa Agung menulis,

37
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,440
dia nampak bersemangat, kacak
dan menyedapkan hati.

38
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:07,600
Itu hanya perkara kecil.

39
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:11,550
Kak Dewi Salji pernah menari
untuk Dewa Agung.

40
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:12,550
Benarkah?

41
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:16,390
Semalam, saya terdengar
muzik ziter Dewa Agung.

42
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,830
Sungguh menyedapkan telinga.

43
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:21,630
Kita dikurniakan rahmat
kerana Yang Amat Mulia,

44
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:23,110
barulah kita berpeluang
untuk dekati Dewa Agung.

45
00:04:23,390 --> 00:04:25,320
Jamuan hampir bermula.

46
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,670
Cepat masuk untuk meraikannya.

47
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:27,790
Betul.

48
00:04:27,950 --> 00:04:29,670
Saya sediakan hadiah yang lebih baik.

49
00:04:29,670 --> 00:04:30,350
Mungkin

50
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:32,350
kita yang dapat main ziter

51
00:04:32,350 --> 00:04:33,200
bersama Dewa Agung hari esok.

52
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:42,110
Selamat hari jadi, Yang Amat Mulia.

53
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:48,040
Bai Jue.

54
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,320
Salam sejahtera, Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

55
00:04:55,270 --> 00:04:56,670
Saya akan suruh Zhi Yang
keluarkan utusan bulu.

56
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,160
Mulai sekarang,

57
00:04:58,550 --> 00:05:00,510
kamu tak dibenarkan
masuk ke Istana Chang Yuan.

58
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,390
Selaku Dewa Utama Camuk,

59
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,074
awak jual saya seperti hadiah

60
00:05:07,075 --> 00:05:09,286
demi barang duniawi seperti ini.

61
00:05:09,286 --> 00:05:10,670
Ini betul-betul bahan jenaka Alam Dewa.

62
00:05:11,716 --> 00:05:12,396
Kamu pun sama.

63
00:05:12,926 --> 00:05:14,486
Bawa pergi benda sekular
dalam tangan kamu.

64
00:05:16,086 --> 00:05:17,316
- Ya.
- Ya.

65
00:05:22,486 --> 00:05:24,086
Ini hadiah saya. Berdasarkan apa
awak buat keputusan?

66
00:05:24,996 --> 00:05:25,526
Betul juga,

67
00:05:25,966 --> 00:05:27,156
saya tak dapat terima

68
00:05:27,276 --> 00:05:28,366
orang yang tak bermoral seperti awak.

69
00:05:29,116 --> 00:05:29,926
Selepas saya pergi ke Alam Bawah,

70
00:05:29,926 --> 00:05:31,366
awak sendiri pergi jelaskan
kepada Zhi Yang.

71
00:05:31,836 --> 00:05:32,556
Jangan berjumpa lagi.

72
00:05:35,436 --> 00:05:36,436
Yang Amat Mulia,
tolong jaga tingkah laku sendiri.

73
00:05:37,116 --> 00:05:37,766
Kali ini,

74
00:05:38,116 --> 00:05:39,766
awak betul-betul hampakan Dewa Agung.

75
00:05:47,926 --> 00:05:48,966
Cukup itu.

76
00:05:49,646 --> 00:05:52,046
Kita dah biasa dengan Dewa Agung
bersikap dingin terhadap kita,

77
00:05:52,316 --> 00:05:53,556
takkan berubah biarpun selepas
sepuluh ribu tahun.

78
00:05:54,116 --> 00:05:55,966
Kali ini, Yang Amat Mulia
dimarahi dengan teruk.

79
00:05:56,766 --> 00:05:58,686
Mengapa pula awak begini sedih?

80
00:05:59,206 --> 00:06:00,596
Dewa... Dewa Agung...

81
00:06:00,876 --> 00:06:03,316
Dewa Agung tak benarkan saya
masuk ke istananya lagi.

82
00:06:06,996 --> 00:06:09,046
Mengapa awak menangis?

83
00:06:09,596 --> 00:06:10,836
Awak tak tahu.

84
00:06:11,206 --> 00:06:13,046
Tadi, Dewa Agung Bai Jue naik marah

85
00:06:13,046 --> 00:06:14,686
di jamuan hari jadi Yang Amat Mulia.

86
00:06:14,966 --> 00:06:16,686
Dia melarang kami
masuk ke Istana Chang Yuan.

87
00:06:19,766 --> 00:06:20,526
Ketulan Ais ini

88
00:06:20,716 --> 00:06:22,046
tak tahu bersikap lembut terhadap gadis.

89
00:06:22,836 --> 00:06:23,396
Kamu

90
00:06:23,686 --> 00:06:24,876
jangan simpan kata-katanya dalam hati.

91
00:06:25,316 --> 00:06:26,276
Keadaan tak sama kali ini.

92
00:06:26,996 --> 00:06:28,716
Dia juga tak sukai Yang Amat Mulia.

93
00:06:28,876 --> 00:06:31,316
Apa? Shang Gu juga kena marah?

94
00:06:41,316 --> 00:06:42,966
Apa masa sekarang?
Awak masih baca buku di sini?

95
00:06:43,246 --> 00:06:45,316
Saya tanya awak. Apa yang telah awak
buat terhadap Shang Gu?

96
00:06:45,646 --> 00:06:46,396
Mengapa saya tak dapat merasai

97
00:06:46,396 --> 00:06:47,596
aura kuasa dewa Shang Gu?

98
00:06:47,876 --> 00:06:49,206
Semasa dia masuk ke Istana Chang Yuan,

99
00:06:49,686 --> 00:06:50,836
saya memeterai kuasa dewanya.

100
00:06:51,156 --> 00:06:51,596
Awak...

101
00:06:53,086 --> 00:06:54,486
Tahukah awak, Shang Gu dah hilang?

102
00:06:55,366 --> 00:06:55,966
Jangan cemas.

103
00:06:56,806 --> 00:06:57,926
Hujan akan turun tak lama kemudian.

104
00:06:58,876 --> 00:07:00,556
Dia tak dapat menanggung kesusahan.

105
00:07:00,836 --> 00:07:02,046
Apabila kena hujan, dia mesti balik.

106
00:07:02,596 --> 00:07:05,116
Bai Jue, apa yang telah
Shang Gu lakukan?

107
00:07:05,486 --> 00:07:06,926
Mengapa awak begini benci akannya?

108
00:07:08,116 --> 00:07:10,686
Buat apa? Dia tamak akan wang
dan barang bernilai.

109
00:07:10,996 --> 00:07:12,686
Cuma beberapa hari bertapa
di istana saya,

110
00:07:13,086 --> 00:07:14,156
tapi dia terima hadiah bernilai
secara terang-terangan,

111
00:07:14,156 --> 00:07:15,436
dan bawa sekumpulan dewi
masuk ke istana saya.

112
00:07:16,526 --> 00:07:17,716
Tak masuk akal.

113
00:07:18,436 --> 00:07:19,396
Hadiah bernilai?

114
00:07:20,806 --> 00:07:23,766
Bai Jue, awak salah faham terhadapnya.

115
00:07:24,206 --> 00:07:25,116
Perbuatan Shang Gu

116
00:07:25,116 --> 00:07:26,686
adalah demi jawab soalan awak,

117
00:07:26,716 --> 00:07:27,926
bukan demi barang bernilai.

118
00:07:34,716 --> 00:07:35,366
Dia dah datang.

119
00:07:38,526 --> 00:07:39,486
Itu Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

120
00:07:39,876 --> 00:07:40,966
Dia betul-betul Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

121
00:07:40,996 --> 00:07:41,526
Betul.

122
00:07:51,556 --> 00:07:53,686
Tempat Luo Cha, ribuan batu panjangnya
dari barat.

123
00:07:54,316 --> 00:07:57,366
Bukit yang senyap,
hampir seribu buah sungai.

124
00:07:58,366 --> 00:07:58,966
Sudah jumpainya!

125
00:08:15,436 --> 00:08:16,686
Betul cakap Tian Qi.

126
00:08:17,316 --> 00:08:18,966
Orang dari Alam Syaitan
baik pembawaan mereka.

127
00:08:19,436 --> 00:08:20,766
Hanya kegembiraan yang sebenar

128
00:08:20,966 --> 00:08:21,836
dapat mempengaruhi mereka.

129
00:08:22,766 --> 00:08:25,276
Maksud awak,
saya salah faham terhadapnya?

130
00:08:26,716 --> 00:08:27,686
Dengar sini,

131
00:08:27,686 --> 00:08:29,206
awak bukan saja perlu cari Shang Gu,

132
00:08:29,246 --> 00:08:30,716
malah, perlu meminta maaf daripada dia
dengan ikhlas.

133
00:08:31,436 --> 00:08:32,926
Itu hari jadinya yang
berusia sepuluh ribu tahun.

134
00:08:33,246 --> 00:08:34,646
Tiada orang dapat bertahan.

135
00:08:35,206 --> 00:08:35,926
Bagaimana meminta maaf?

136
00:08:37,366 --> 00:08:38,806
Saya dah makan buah pic hari jadi awak.

137
00:08:40,516 --> 00:08:41,156
Sungguh manis, bukan?

138
00:08:42,756 --> 00:08:44,246
Pahit dan keras seperti awak.

139
00:08:44,686 --> 00:08:45,716
Adakah awak kehilangan deria rasa?

140
00:08:47,246 --> 00:08:49,156
Pendek kata, saya dah fikir cara
untuk awak.

141
00:08:49,486 --> 00:08:50,516
Bukankah awak suka batu berukir?

142
00:08:50,926 --> 00:08:52,716
Ukirlah rantai tangan batu berukir
untuk dia.

143
00:08:52,716 --> 00:08:54,126
Gadis suka barang kemas.

144
00:08:56,926 --> 00:08:58,006
Jangan berpura-pura tak dengar.

145
00:08:58,716 --> 00:09:00,126
Saya cakap dengan awak,

146
00:09:00,326 --> 00:09:01,956
awak perlu pujuk Shang Gu.

147
00:09:02,126 --> 00:09:02,756
Jika tak, saya...

148
00:09:04,516 --> 00:09:05,006
Saya...

149
00:09:06,836 --> 00:09:07,396
Dewa Agung Tian Qi.

150
00:09:07,396 --> 00:09:08,596
Dewa Agung konon.

151
00:09:08,756 --> 00:09:09,366
Mari sini.

152
00:09:10,486 --> 00:09:10,886
Dewa Agung Tian Qi.

153
00:09:10,886 --> 00:09:12,486
Saya akan heret raksasa api awak
ke Istana Tai Chu

154
00:09:12,486 --> 00:09:13,486
dan memanaskan arak
untuk saya setiap hari.

155
00:09:13,806 --> 00:09:14,486
Dewa Agung Tian Qi, awak...

156
00:09:14,486 --> 00:09:15,126
Awak apa?

157
00:09:28,636 --> 00:09:31,156
Dewa Agung, kita perlu cari
Yang Amat Mulia.

158
00:09:31,566 --> 00:09:32,956
Kalau hujan lebat

159
00:09:33,366 --> 00:09:34,516
dan kuasa rohani dimeterai,

160
00:09:34,756 --> 00:09:35,196
dia akan...

161
00:09:48,076 --> 00:09:49,246
Mengapa tak berteduh di dalam?

162
00:09:50,566 --> 00:09:51,956
Kasihani sendiri atau
meneliti kesalahan sendiri?

163
00:09:55,806 --> 00:09:57,006
Bukankah awak kata jangan berjumpa lagi?

164
00:09:57,366 --> 00:09:58,246
Mengapa datang jumpa saya lagi?

165
00:09:58,486 --> 00:09:59,326
Pulangkan kuasa dewa kepada saya.

166
00:10:02,566 --> 00:10:03,196
Dewa

167
00:10:03,716 --> 00:10:04,836
unik seperti gunung dan sungai,

168
00:10:05,006 --> 00:10:05,886
hidup lama seperti masa.

169
00:10:06,486 --> 00:10:07,366
Namun, kalau kuasa rohani dimeterai,

170
00:10:07,636 --> 00:10:08,756
awak hanya orang biasa.

171
00:10:09,486 --> 00:10:11,516
Pakailah. Jangan kena selesema.

172
00:10:13,686 --> 00:10:15,006
Adakah awak meminta maaf daripada saya?

173
00:10:15,276 --> 00:10:16,246
Bolehkah awak maafkan saya?

174
00:10:16,516 --> 00:10:18,396
Berdasarkan mantel ini? Jangan harap.

175
00:10:19,596 --> 00:10:21,886
Hutan Darah Merah terletak di
persimpangan Alam Dewa dan Alam Iblis.

176
00:10:22,196 --> 00:10:23,196
Peperangan pada 70 ribu tahun lalu

177
00:10:23,486 --> 00:10:24,836
menyebabkan tempat ini
amat kurang kuasa rohani.

178
00:10:25,076 --> 00:10:25,756
Cara awak

179
00:10:26,156 --> 00:10:28,046
hanya dapat buat Puak Syaitan Harimau
gembira untuk seketika,

180
00:10:28,366 --> 00:10:29,486
tak dapat kekal aman sepanjang hayat.

181
00:10:30,156 --> 00:10:31,076
Saya dah tanya Tian Qi.

182
00:10:31,836 --> 00:10:32,716
Dia tak dapat lakukannya pun,

183
00:10:32,716 --> 00:10:33,566
awak pula suruh saya lakukan.

184
00:10:33,636 --> 00:10:34,756
Jelasnya, awak menyusahkan saya.

185
00:10:35,446 --> 00:10:36,326
Tian Qi memang tak dapat lakukannya,

186
00:10:36,756 --> 00:10:37,756
begitu juga dengan saya dan Zhi Yang.

187
00:10:38,196 --> 00:10:39,006
Namun, awak pula dapat lakukannya.

188
00:10:39,366 --> 00:10:39,956
Saya?

189
00:10:41,446 --> 00:10:44,246
Cuma awak yang dapat menjamin kedamaian
tiga alam selama sepuluh ribu tahun.

190
00:10:44,716 --> 00:10:46,926
Cuma awak yang dapat buat Puak
Syaitan Harimau hidup gembira dan aman.

191
00:10:47,246 --> 00:10:49,196
Ini ujian pertama yang saya
beri kepada awak,

192
00:10:49,276 --> 00:10:51,366
juga tugas sepanjang hayat
sebagai dewa utama tiga alam.

193
00:10:53,276 --> 00:10:54,636
Saya ingat awak pandang rendah
terhadap saya.

194
00:10:54,956 --> 00:10:56,486
Zhi Yang tak benarkan saya
sentuh warkah pun.

195
00:11:03,006 --> 00:11:03,806
Jamuan hari jadi saya

196
00:11:03,806 --> 00:11:05,636
berkelas tinggi selama ini.

197
00:11:05,836 --> 00:11:06,856
Dewa yang hadiri jamuan

198
00:11:07,446 --> 00:11:09,516
tak dapat masuk
kalau tak bawa barang bernilai.

199
00:11:09,956 --> 00:11:11,276
Selaku Dewa Sejati Bai Jue,

200
00:11:11,486 --> 00:11:13,396
murahnya hadiah awak.

201
00:11:22,756 --> 00:11:23,326
Cukup?

202
00:11:32,886 --> 00:11:34,246
(Tak sangka Ketulan Ais)

203
00:11:34,806 --> 00:11:36,126
(akan memujuk saya.)

204
00:11:39,806 --> 00:11:42,686
(Peluang ini jarang dijumpai.
Saya perlu lepaskan kemarahan saya.)

205
00:11:46,836 --> 00:11:48,156
Saya Dewa Utama Tiga Alam.

206
00:11:48,596 --> 00:11:49,326
Tak kira betapa tak gunanya saya,

207
00:11:49,396 --> 00:11:51,126
orang lain hanya berani bercakap
di belakang saya.

208
00:11:51,636 --> 00:11:52,446
Awak pula berlainan,

209
00:11:52,596 --> 00:11:54,196
berkali-kali menghina saya
di depan khalayak ramai.

210
00:11:56,446 --> 00:11:57,446
Apa yang boleh saya buat?

211
00:11:59,926 --> 00:12:01,196
Saya bukan orang yang berfikiran sempit.

212
00:12:01,806 --> 00:12:03,926
Beginilah. Awak memeterai
kuasa dewa sendiri

213
00:12:04,326 --> 00:12:04,956
untuk setengah jam.

214
00:12:06,756 --> 00:12:07,276
Tak ada masalah.

215
00:12:21,566 --> 00:12:23,446
Serangan ini dianggap tak terhutang pada
satu sama lain.

216
00:12:31,046 --> 00:12:32,396
Awak memeterai kuasa dewa sendiri

217
00:12:32,686 --> 00:12:33,326
untuk setengah jam.

218
00:12:34,246 --> 00:12:34,756
Tak ada masalah.

219
00:12:47,926 --> 00:12:48,806
Mustahil ini.

220
00:12:49,196 --> 00:12:50,366
Awak dah memeterai kuasa dewa sendiri.

221
00:12:51,126 --> 00:12:51,836
Sudahkah kita tak berhutang kepada
satu sama lain?

222
00:12:52,156 --> 00:12:52,926
Awak pasti menipu.

223
00:12:53,636 --> 00:12:55,806
Tanpa kuasa dewa,
awak juga orang biasa.

224
00:12:56,126 --> 00:12:57,006
Saya tak percaya.

225
00:13:05,886 --> 00:13:06,446
Percaya sekarang?

226
00:13:07,366 --> 00:13:08,926
Sepanjang hayat ini panjang,
dunia ini besar dan luas.

227
00:13:09,596 --> 00:13:11,566
Apabila awak jadi Dewa Utama Camuk
suatu hari nanti,

228
00:13:12,156 --> 00:13:13,886
segala-gala di tiga alam bagi awak

229
00:13:14,156 --> 00:13:15,886
mungkin akan mempunyai peraturan
dan makna yang baharu.

230
00:13:17,326 --> 00:13:18,046
Sekarang dah lewat.

231
00:13:18,686 --> 00:13:20,396
Yang Amat Mulia, berehatlah awal.

232
